<m0>The dying speak;<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 2.75 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>AIDS czar listens<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 2.40 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.152 INCHES<m2><ql>
